MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

95-1371. Natanski v. Prudential Property.

Summit County, No. 17020. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Summit County. Upon consideration of appellants’ application for dismissal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application for dismissal be, and hereby is, granted.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
